name: Divinos IT Solutions Pvt Ltd
overview:
Divinos is a custom software development company focusing on strategic initiatives of customers, offering full life cycle customization software programming services. We provide various services including concept development, software development, support and enhancements that meet the requirements of clients and customers.

Divinos is an ISO 9001-2008 certified, headquartered in Hyderabad, India with modern competency center. With Divinos Delivery Model (DDM) we serve global clientele and Government Agencies.

Our expertise is in business process improvement, e-Business solutions, upgrades and testing. Our application management and support helps return on investment (ROI) and reduces total cost of owner-ship (TCO).
